fields.title: Xbox Series X
fields.description: The fastest, most powerful Xbox ever. Explore rich new worlds with 12 teraflops of raw graphic processing power, DirectX ray tracing, a custom SSD, and 4K gaming

fields.title: Playstation 5
fields.description: The PS5 console unleashes new gaming possibilities that you never anticipated. Experience lightning fast loading with an ultra-high speed SSD, deeper immersion with support for haptic feedback, adaptive triggers, and 3D Audio, and an all-new generation of incredible PlayStation games.

fields.title: Nintendo Switch
fields.description: The Nintendo Switch is a hybrid video game console, consisting of a console unit, a dock, and two Joy-Con controllers.
